Package shibboleth.data

The data package contains all classes to retrieve data, such as data from the Github API and stored data in a database.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DataSource
    This interface represents a source which can provide Github artifacts.
    DataStore
    This class extends a DataSource in order to provide write functionality to a source.
    RepoFilter
    A utility class for filtering repos based on their properties.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CachedSource
    A CachedSource can be used to 'chain' a DataStore on top of a DataSource.
    CachedStore
    A CachedSource can be used to 'chain' a DataStore on top of another DataStore.
    CrawlSource
    A DataSource optimized for crawling.
    HashMapStore
    A Github Data Store that stores Github objects in HashMaps and Lists.
    JavaScriptFilter
    A filter that only accepts projects which are written in JavaScript.
    ReadOnlyCachedSource
    This class provides the same functionality as the CachedSource, but with the difference that the cache is treated read only.
    TransparantFilter
    A filter which accepts all projects.

Package shibboleth.data Description

The data package contains all classes to retrieve data, such as data from the Github API and stored data in a database.
